node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Ellen Alexander on April 27, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and footwear.

node.text:
I wanna post those memories from my Camden appartment I used to live at. It is Hollywood. I liked that area- many influencers live there in that building. We were constantly exchanging ideas and having friendly chats in elevators and common areas which were plenty.
I moved there because of my girlfriend whom I barely saw ones I moved to appartment right above her.  Young crowd in the building were constantly  partying in the patio- groups of people were always hanging by fireplace and at the pool cabanas. Julia took those beautiful pictures. I miss having my long eyelashes 😅 it helped looking all made up and fancy with literally no efforts. @juliamindarphoto
